322
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:14,080
Poďme konečne na to.

323
00:42:19,990 --> 00:42:22,090
Počkáme ešte chvíľu?

324
00:42:23,090 --> 00:42:25,790
Nie, budeme meškať, poďme.

325
00:42:43,610 --> 00:42:46,410
Dámy a páni, vitajte!

326
00:42:46,410 --> 00:42:50,720
Som DJ Yoo Hyung z Music Dial.

327
00:42:58,720 --> 00:43:01,930
Máme pre Vás pripravenú, Vami očakávanú ...

328
00:43:01,930 --> 00:43:06,230
